sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Mgr as PPC Manager
    participant AI as AI Agent
    participant Ads as Live Google Ads<br/>Account

    Mgr->>AI: Request a change — pause keywords,<br/>edit budgets, rename ad groups
    AI->>AI: Build the mutation — but do NOT run it
    AI-->>Mgr: DRY-RUN PREVIEW — target account,<br/>current vs proposed,<br/>count, reversibility
    Note over Mgr,Ads: Nothing has touched the live account yet.<br/>The preview is the whole point.

    alt Human approves
        Mgr->>AI: Explicit approval — typed by the human,<br/>never generated by the AI
        AI->>Ads: Execute exactly what was previewed
        Ads-->>AI: Confirmed
        AI-->>Mgr: Done — mutation logged<br/>for the audit trail
    else Human declines
        Mgr->>AI: Cancel
        AI-->>Mgr: Nothing executed. Account untouched.
    end
